Ranger Help for: conduct
========================

SUMMARY:
Rangers live by a code rooted in respect for the natural world. A
Ranger protects the wild places and the creatures within them, hunting
only when necessary and never destroying what is not needed.

Rangers are expected to maintain a neutral alignment. Straying too far
toward good or evil increases the cost of performing skills, as Gaia
favors balance in all things. Aid your fellow Rangers when you can,
and respect the bond between a Ranger and their animal follower.

Do not abuse the gifts Gaia has granted. Use the land wisely, take
only what you need, and leave the wilderness as you found it. A true
Ranger is a guardian first, a hunter second.

